AIO Phase-1 Monorepo

This repo launches the AIO Phase-1 core:

Escrow with WorkReceipts (on-chain events)

Receipts sealing via Merkle-sum monthly root (oracle quorum)

Oracle registry with bonds/unbond delays/penalties

Governance (Elders) minimal multisig + mode guards

